Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}艾利斯家 庭园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这招呼打的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说传闻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我可是小有名气的英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾利斯家请我来的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我请他来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 席恩·阿斯塔尔君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾利斯家的主人 露西尔·艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日请你来不为他事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想听听你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在将问你几个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:01:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些问题是为了判断你是否有资格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在提问之前 我有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你的答案不能令人满意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 不会有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至不会感觉到自己的脑袋和身体分了家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情似乎觉得难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这里可是艾利斯家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩·阿斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代代只侍奉王者的家门之主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要试探我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本国的始祖 阿斯路德·罗兰德的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部拥有这种资格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是下贱的狗杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我就听听你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 露西尔·艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易从战场捡回来的命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算扔在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易捡回来的命更应如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:33.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}眠り解きあぐねて　君を見失い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:33.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}漫长沉睡中醒来 却发现失去了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:38.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}壊したくなる今すべて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:38.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}此刻恨不能破坏一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:46.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}望む言葉が二度と聞けないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:46.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}若再也听不到 那令人心动的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:52.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}命さえ無為に差し出すでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:52.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我宁愿徒然付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:03:00.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}消えそうな輝きへと寄り添う想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:03:00.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心绪飘向那若隐若现的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:07.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}孤独だよ　私の元にも朝日がくるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:07.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一阵孤独 是否我亦能拥有明日朝阳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:14.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}答えて…ふたりを繋ぐ愛があると
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:14.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}告诉我 我们之间还有爱相连
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:21.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}招かれた絶望の果てに立ち向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:21.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}让我能直面眼前那无尽绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:28.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}産まれて滅びる人の意識こそが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:28.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}正是生而即逝的人之意识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:38.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}未来を選び　鍵を開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:38.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}才能选择未来 打开那心锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}罗兰德 城下城区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵大人要过路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德 高等收监所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能早点回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 有新来的囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他习惯之前暂时得晚点回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他干了什么 真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进了这里可就永不见天日了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次出来时怕就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是年轻人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还不满20的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 看守大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你提再多次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}莱纳·报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能给你高级棉被或者羽毛被什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你今天又想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸和铅笔 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有个王立军事特殊学院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你从那里的图书馆帮我借点书来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点东西倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加起来大概30本左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3、30本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这里织网
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活不活得下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是连只苍蝇都没有的牢房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么硬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 分你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢啦 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收集这么多书 每天都在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能麻烦你再加借个10本左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 还没睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人在这昏暗诡异的环境下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就神经错乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多闹腾的家伙 过个一星期都会变得沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一个月大都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 这是今天的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 3Q
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王立特殊学院之后是阿斯路德纪念图书馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会过阵子全国的图书馆都搬这儿来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家闺女 感冒好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 活蹦乱跳的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她终于能自己站起来走路了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 那可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 一想到这孩子终于也长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就感动得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子长起来真是不等人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是刚会走路而已 说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就这样 等到她长大成人出嫁那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事绝不容许
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是看上我家闺女了吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想等大叔的闺女长大时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还有战争 你也不乐意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪有父母会心甘情愿送子女上战场的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争到底是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 今天好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天稍微奢侈点 是蒜蓉鸡肉吉士烤三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是每天都得忍受淡得跟水一样的汤哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近老婆生意做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人还是要吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你家两口子都挣钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 老婆在早市帮人卖蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有吃奶的孩子 真不想让她去干活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总比当兵好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前有场大战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我也在军队里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拉上战场 伙伴们都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是受够战争了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我辞了队长的官 来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然生活苦了点 不过我不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 好高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所选择的道路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为能在这里永远午睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是够古怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿不比这里亮堂多粮好过活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛老待在这儿不走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨 还以为要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子再不整理一下真要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总之先吃个早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡个回笼觉之后再慢慢整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 正等你呢大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 又和老婆吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是闺女介绍男朋友给你了所以很失落？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道 我闺女才三岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的三岁小孩可牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你是说哪方面牛 我家闺女可不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个家长都是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 不是因为这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啦 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我的早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那啥 我的死刑定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这国家总算养怪物养怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢 放我多活了差不多两年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里写的研究报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一起带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…命令书上说禁止带任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 马上要死的人也不需要那玩意儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭丧着脸了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 你保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是莱纳·琉特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸事承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这位美女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事色情狂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话能不能问问您为什么叫我色情狂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有经历
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事我听说了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我要在这里逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 竟想和我打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前跟人约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开 开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我不动真格的怕是真要死在她手里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这么说刚才那下不是真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也就七成功力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 怪不得那家伙想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 寄宿沉眠于大地的恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能跟上这魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用了什么法术…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有？什么也没？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用任何魔法还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求水云
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩雨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才手下留情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不用水而用可大范围攻击的火炎魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能击中我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 但是那样你说不定会死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得这么漂亮的脸蛋 烧伤了也很可惜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摧枯拉朽的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你这个色情狂在战斗中满脑子邪恶妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致无法做出正确判断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧枯拉朽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 王正在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有人会乖乖走过去行刑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 你一定会悔青了肠子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德 城下町
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这国家到底发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临我的宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了 今天先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么说也是国王殿前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管 我很困
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 觉得他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个超乎想象的色情狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若置之不理 数年之内必会犯下可怕的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被兄长以外的人手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也适可而止吧 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然不告诉你姬珐的消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐把你托付给我就离开了这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是想四处巡游多看看这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:18:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 今天请你来不是为了告诉你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的报告？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“如何建立午睡王国”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题虽然胡来 内容却着实有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的勇者遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那无法衡量的强大威力用作抑制力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除全世界的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 亏你想得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便看人家的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意这报告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在立刻去巡游世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那勇者遗物全部给我收集来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？为啥要我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 光是莱纳去我担心你会偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望菲莉丝作为他的辅佐一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了打发时间才写了那报告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听我的命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是受兄长之命才协助你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是你的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔已经同意了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼曰：
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝若不听话 就立马拆了维尼特团子店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两分钟内启程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了色情狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 丢脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二 丢身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩你小子给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于肯去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁肯去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说这声音是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 莱纳交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要随便决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了走吧 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你搭档啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所前往的目的地 是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是未来之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方并非你的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我还不会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王为物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国家的一个齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会破坏新齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还很新呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会走我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 你所选择的道路是这条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和我相异
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌人死 也讨厌杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌让人哭 也讨厌哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可选择的人生 会是怎样心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去至亲 失去至爱又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不希望这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何世界却总笑着追求这种无意义的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未想过勉强去改变什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不改变又很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想再失去任何东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该向前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直故意视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会直面自己的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了创造一个谁也不会再失去任何东西的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩 姬珐不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伊尔 托尼 珐露不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩也不用再自寻烦恼的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家欢笑着 只要睡睡午觉就好的…世界
